## Shoegaze x Dream Pop
Add: pastel wash, airy glow, softer contrast, floral blur, “floaty light”
Avoid: heavy glitch, harsh noise artifacts
Use: haze_pastel palette + MODULE_lighting

## Shoegaze x Hauntology
Add: degraded media, archive dust, faded signage, tape-warp mood, ghost typography
Use: sepia_zine palette + paper_xerox_zine textures

## Shoegaze x Vaporwave
Add: chrome gradients, mall afterlife lighting, neon fog, marble + plastic
Keep shoegaze: still low-clarity + bloom + grain (don’t become clean 3D)

## Shoegaze x Glitch / Noise
Add: macroblock scars, alias stair-steps, datamosh smear, scanlines
Rule: glitches should be “in the haze,” not crisp geometric UI


