# Shoegaze Style

Shoegaze-as-visual: wall-of-texture, dreamy diffusion, nostalgic grain, optional interference math.

## Use it in 20 seconds
1) Pick a preset: gentle_gaze / heavy_gaze / total_wall
2) Provide a subject
3) Compile: subject + modules + palette + negatives

## Entrypoints
- style/shoegaze.style.yaml (canonical)
- recipes/quickstart_prompts.md (copy/paste prompts)
- shaders/mapping.yaml (shader knobs)

## Modules (toggles)
- Core / Light / Texture / Composition (default on)
- Interference / Materials / Typography / Album Layout (optional)

## Golden rules
Field > subject, soft boundaries, layer stack, memory materials.


