# Style Dials (Shoegaze)

## Dial: Clarity (0 → 1)
- 0.1: subject mostly implied
- 0.3: eyes or one highlight is crisp
- 0.6: too clean; you're leaving shoegaze territory

## Dial: Interference (0 → 1)
- 0.1: shimmer only (suggestion)
- 0.4: visible moiré/phase drift
- 0.7: "total wall" (must be fused into haze)

## Dial: Memory Material
Pick at least one:
- film (halation + dust)
- paper (fiber + misregistration)
- signal (CRT scanlines + smear)

## Dial: Focal Anchor
Always choose ONE:
- eyes
- streetlight
- single sharp edge
- bright specular highlight


